tynina for the most by any woman in any Olympic sport.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 394, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.7643028318556339, \"rank\": 0.2838802648587533, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999999999413376, \"rank\": 5.848123801475162e-11, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 444, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.270687545453379e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"score\": 0.9999999999681677, \"rank\": 1.9810119237002482e-11, \"text\": \"Soviet\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Soviet_Union\"}, {\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prince\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"the home nation\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"four spectacular gold medals\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngr